ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: recommend, this is a good course

It's English course which gives you opportunities to talk in English. I recommend it to the fellow students especially those who just come to US, since this course provides you the chance to get new friends and practice oral English.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course help me lay a good foundation in English speaking which is essential for my communication with labmates and giving scientific presentations.
Gives us a perfect environment to learn how to speak English. It expands our vocabulary and shift us towards a native speaker level.
